# Main Runtime Rules (Figma Plugin API)

- `src/main` code runs in the Figma plugin context; keep logic independent from React/UI libraries.
- Use async-safe Plugin API patterns where required (file data can be lazily loaded).
- Communicate with UI only via typed event handlers from `src/types.ts`.
- Avoid hidden side effects: import/export/docs commands should report status and errors back to UI.
- For docs generation, update existing root docs frame when present; create only when missing.
